2005-11-29  James Livingston  <jrl@ids.org.au>

	* data/ui/rhythmbox-ui.xml:
	* sources/rb-podcast-source.c:
	(rb_podcast_source_songs_show_popup_cb),
	(rb_podcast_source_cmd_download_post),
